# Spaghetti Cacio e Pepe

> Tbd 

- Spaghetti Noodles |  |

Cook spaghetti according to package

Reserve 1 cup pasta water

## The Goods

- Pancetta | 1/4 lbs | 

Crisp for 7 to 9 minutes

- Olive Oil | 1/4 cup | 
- Garlic | 4 cloves | Minced
- Red Pepper Flakes | 1 tsp | 
- Black Pepper | 2 tsp | 

Cook until fragrant (1 minute)

## Putting it Together

- Lemons | 1/4 cup | Juice
- Parmesan (Parmigiano-Reggiano) | 1.5 cups | 

Combine everything, use small increments of pasta water until coated

- Baby Arugula | 3 cups | 

Serve once arugula wilts

> Source: Cravings by Chrissy Teigen
